Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.54,0:03:41.78,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}不要害怕
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.49,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}拚命划
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.77,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}把他們推到旋渦裡去
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.26,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}浪的流向對我們有利
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.51,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}進攻進攻
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.12,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}你怎麼看
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.40,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}形勢對我們有利
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.69,0:04:12.99,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}把弓給我
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.02,0:04:27.24,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}母親 我想觀戰
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.60,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}很危險
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.04,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}但是我想看
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.43,0:04:37.29,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}如果中箭也不會哭的話
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.39,0:04:38.09,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}就可以看
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.32,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}你一定怕痛吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.23,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.74,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}就這樣擊潰源氏
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.31,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}衝啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.57,0:05:06.49,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}義經大人 船在往後漂 無法前進
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.61,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}現在可能需要撤退
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.43,0:05:12.58,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}兵力上我們占優
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.92,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}時間一長平家的士兵就會疲勞
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.27,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}請暫時忍耐一下
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.85,0:05:28.71,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}這是…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.31,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}那是？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.23,0:05:46.95,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}這是…
