Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.28,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}不要過來
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.53,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}這個髮型很適合你
