Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.17,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}我們勢頭正盛
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.57,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}進攻進攻
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.78,0:07:54.89,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}這可不得了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.58,Dial-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1}還是去母親的船上
